Is it in gratitude or with gratitude?

Gratitude is an emotion expressing appreciation for what one has. It is a recognition of value independent of monetary worth. Spontaneously generated from within, it is an affirmation of goodness. Research shows that people differ in the degree to which they are inclined to experience and express gratitude.
